race.comment: GOLDEN GANGSTER (1) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 1.5 lengths third (20.18) behind Cool It Mister at this track. Expected to feature in the finish again. KAISON'S CURSE (8) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Other winner three back (20.03) at this track over 342m. Well placed here and should do much better. RITZA RIOT (4) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only one length (20.15) behind Cool It Mister at this track. Bold showing expected. SMOOTH VIXEN (2) won as favourite last time and another big run is on the cards.
